Package: inkaR
Title: Download and Analyze INKAR Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Furkan", "Coban", , "email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight package to download spatial development indicators 
    from the BBSR INKAR database. Provides a modern interface using 'httr2' 
    and handles metadata lookup including bilingual support (DE/EN).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: 
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    tibble,
    dplyr,
    rlang,
    tidyr
Suggests: 
    readxl,
    testthat
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
